    "name": "Dagada's Story",
    "steam_appid": 1859390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/8580c517ee3898b4048ded313d44c168.avif?t=1772059740\" width=682 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an adventure inspired by the games of the Super Nintendo era!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accidentally stranded on a planet with a hostile climate, Dagada awakens alone in a dark cave, guided by a strange voice showing him the way... An entire village comes to his aid, helping him repair his spaceship and return home. As he explores the mountain, Dagada uncovers the catastrophe threatening the village and must overcome challenges to protect his new friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/f9f58a6863b597998f2269281b68bcec.poster.avif?t=1772059740\" width=450 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/f9f58a6863b597998f2269281b68bcec.webm?t=1772059740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/f9f58a6863b597998f2269281b68bcec.mp4?t=1772059740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dagada</strong> can jump, climb, and push heavy objects to explore the mountain, while <strong>Naou</strong> can fly and use energy to activate mysterious stones. Together, they will explore dark caves and solve mysterious puzzles in ancient ruins to help Dagada return home. But the threat of a dangerous climate looms! Will you help them restore harmony to this once peaceful nature turned hostile?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/5c44e2c76ea2e6198dd1d0aa470148f5.poster.avif?t=1772059740\" width=452 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/5c44e2c76ea2e6198dd1d0aa470148f5.webm?t=1772059740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/5c44e2c76ea2e6198dd1d0aa470148f5.mp4?t=1772059740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 worlds to explore and a village to rest in</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alternate between 2 playable characters to solve puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the necessary parts to repair broken objects scattered throughout the world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple day and night system to explore locations in different ways</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Side quests and secrets to uncover more about the characters and the game’s universe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful pixel-art graphics and animations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the world at your own pace to create your own experience</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/281bf8ea6975b51d2e7ba2241b5350e8.poster.avif?t=1772059740\" width=450 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/281bf8ea6975b51d2e7ba2241b5350e8.webm?t=1772059740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859390/extras/281bf8ea6975b51d2e7ba2241b5350e8.mp4?t=1772059740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
